{"type": "article", "id": 18865, "title": "nendo 设计的眼镜框", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-11T08:52:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143046nxG7T53pvLlEIrmS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是 nendo 为日本眼镜品牌 ZEROGRA 设计的眼镜框，在镜框的转折处有一个向内的“C”字型结构，能让镜框更容易开合。当它完全打开时，就形成了一个小的圆环，也不会影响到视线。nendo 经过反复实验确保这种结构能持久使用。此外，他们还设计眼镜盒和用于展示眼镜的圆环，镜架插在中间，就像插进了鹅卵石里，很特别。</span><a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/zerogra-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143044f8aHjyAd0YXnI4V7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143045wWJGRHt2pj70UNfZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143045rdURpt6n81gzlbAL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60790598\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143046rok0yj9hE5uSJ7bq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143046DMQcmCn6afrTgVoe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}